dec: Two outfits fight for exclusive import rights at Los Santos Int
ernational. Get as much of your rival's product back to your ba
se of operations as you can, while they try to do the same. Be
careful though, you'll only have Airtugs for transport if you m
iss out on the three choppers in no man's land.
